Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We start all the lectures with a glory and excelsis deo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If that makes you nervous, this is the wrong lecture to be on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.77,0:01:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Having been forewarned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, today we're talking about reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality, as everyone knows, is a crutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Our modern society pays no attention to it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.86,0:01:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you can't make political hay out of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.54,0:01:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Only out of distortions of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, anyway, everyone presumes that they understand what reality is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.04,0:01:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And we asked everyone in the room, do you comprehend reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.26,0:01:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody here say no?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If they don't comprehend reality?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a room full of idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this lecture and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The next one has to do with truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This one has to do with reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.61,0:02:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality is more concrete, literal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with content.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.76,0:02:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth has to do with context.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.28,0:02:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What one derives from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we've got some interesting slides, which I hope you like, because I slaved over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.57,0:02:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We've given about 100 lectures worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,100.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.76,0:02:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Over 50 here in Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll be approaching our 100th lecture birthday soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll give out free ice cream cones, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.56,0:02:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's start with the first lecture, which will, I mean, the first slide, which will remind me what we're talking about today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.40,0:02:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.02,0:02:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.62,0:02:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we need to know how many people here are new.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people are new?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.17,0:02:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there is, there is some.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's new people, we always do a brief review of the basics, just so that you have an orientation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.72,0:03:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we go on to the new material.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we have a few review slides.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And as soon as I can, oh, there she goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.71,0:03:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The map of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And we remembered our pointer today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The map of consciousness is probably, you know, pretty well known worldwide.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That reality, everything that exists radiates forth an energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And that energy can be picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,By the field of consciousness itself, which is non-linear, beyond form, everywhere present, throughout all of time, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's our point of reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It constitutes the absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, a lot of people have a negative idea about absolutism.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.28,0:04:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And they are absolutely convinced that absolutism is false.
