Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.77,1:06:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think, I just don't have, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.41,1:06:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.63,1:06:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to think about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.83,1:06:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.78,1:06:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All you can say is what you've heard.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.51,1:06:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.35,1:06:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you see, that's a different dimension.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.01,1:06:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard such and such.
