Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.64,1:06:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard thus and so.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.20,1:06:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even spiritual knowledge, all you can say, I have heard.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.72,1:06:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have heard, you see, is a much more humble position.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.04,1:06:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard that such and such is so.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.96,1:06:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, through my own inner work, I will arrive
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.08,1:06:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,at whether or not I have heard such and such.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.84,1:06:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether that is true or not, you know.
