Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.43,1:06:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and those who cannot hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.02,1:06:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, lectures such as the one here are heard by some
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.08,1:06:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and not heard by others.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.94,1:07:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, the other dictum that went with it is that those
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.14,1:07:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,who can hear, hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.41,1:07:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't worry about those who cannot hear,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.95,1:07:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that's god's problem.
