Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.22,1:10:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the two are aligned with peace, and therefore the decision that is made
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.86,1:10:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,is one that tries to resolve issues rather than prolong them or inflame them further.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.59,1:10:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So content, then, is our understanding of content depends on the context,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.57,1:10:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,whether a certain thing is right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.21,1:11:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So today's world, what you see is a struggle for moral superiority.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.01,1:11:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Moral superiority.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.97,1:11:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all this world is about.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.64,1:11:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's right and who has the moral high ground.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.13,1:11:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't think I have the moral high ground, I'll kill you.
