Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.86,1:11:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see, it's constant.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.04,1:11:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The evening news is comical,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.90,1:11:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,which everything is twisted a little bit to give it a moral high ground twist, you know, moral high ground.
