Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.46,1:12:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.98,1:12:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The awareness of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.88,1:12:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And by observation and mindfulness, you see the mind taking off in these various directions.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.61,1:13:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So mindfulness is then a spiritual practice to be aware of where you are at all times.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.54,1:13:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,To be aware of what your mind is doing.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.54,1:13:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, eventually, as you let go of everything and through contemplation,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.63,1:13:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you begin to realize what the mind is, you see.
